# Schedula - Complete API Collection (Day 1-13)

Base URL: http://localhost:3000

---

## 🔐 AUTH APIs

### 1. Signup Doctor
POST /signup
Body:
{
  "name": "Dr. Mohamed",
  "email": "doctor@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "DOCTOR"
}

### 2. Signup Patient
POST /signup
Body:
{
  "name": "Patient Name",
  "email": "patient@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "PATIENT"
}

### 3. Login Doctor
POST /login
Body:
{
  "email": "doctor@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Login Patient
POST /login
Body:
{
  "email": "patient@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

---

## 👨‍⚕️ DOCTOR PROFILE APIs

### 5. Create Doctor Profile
POST /doctor/profile (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "fullName": "Dr. Mohamed",
  "specialization": "Cardiologist",
  "qualification": "MBBS, MD",
  "experience": "10 years",
  "consultationFee": "700",
  "consultationHours": "9AM - 5PM",
  "bio": "Heart specialist",
  "phone": "9876544444",
  "isAvailable": true
}

### 6. Get Doctor Profile
GET /doctor/my/profile (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 7. Update Doctor Profile
PATCH /doctor/my/profile (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "consultationFee": "800"
}

---

## 🧑‍⚕️ PATIENT PROFILE APIs

### 8. Create Patient Profile
POST /patient/profile (Bearer: Patient Token)
Body:
{
  "fullName": "Patient Name",
  "age": "25",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phone": "9876544444",
  "address": "Madurai, Tamil Nadu",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "medicalHistory": "None"
}

### 9. Get Patient Profile
GET /patient/profile (Bearer: Patient Token)

### 10. Update Patient Profile
PATCH /patient/profile (Bearer: Patient Token)
Body:
{
  "address": "Chennai, Tamil Nadu"
}

---

## 🔍 DOCTOR DISCOVERY APIs

### 11. Get All Doctors
GET /doctor

### 12. Filter by Specialization
GET /doctor?specialization=Cardiologist

### 13. Search by Name
GET /doctor?search=Mohamed

### 14. Pagination
GET /doctor?page=1&limit=10

### 15. Filter by Availability
GET /doctor?availability=true

### 16. Get Doctor by ID
GET /doctor/:id

---

## 📅 AVAILABILITY APIs

### 17. Create Recurring Availability
POST /doctor/availability (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "dayOfWeek": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "12:00:00"
}

### 18. Get Availability
GET /doctor/availability (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 19. Update Availability
PATCH /doctor/availability/:id (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "13:00:00"
}

### 20. Delete Availability
DELETE /doctor/availability/:id (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 21. Custom Override
POST /doctor/availability/override (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "date": "2026-06-20",
  "startTime": "14:00:00",
  "endTime": "16:00:00"
}

### 22. Get Availability by Date
GET /doctor/availability/date?date=2026-06-20 (Bearer: Doctor Token)

---

## 🕐 SCHEDULING APIs

### 23. Set Scheduling Type
POST /doctor/scheduling-type (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "schedulingType": "STREAM"
}

### 24. Generate Stream Slots
POST /doctor/slots/stream (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "date": "2026-06-22",
  "duration": 15,
  "bufferTime": 5
}

### 25. Generate Wave Slots
POST /doctor/slots/wave (Bearer: Doctor Token)
Body:
{
  "date": "2026-06-23",
  "maxCapacity": 5
}

### 26. Patient Views Scheduled Slots
GET /doctor/:doctorId/slots/scheduled?date=2026-06-22 (Bearer: Patient Token)

### 27. Generate Slots (Legacy)
POST /doctor/slots/generate?date=2026-06-22&duration=30 (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 28. Patient Views Slots (Legacy)
GET /doctor/:doctorId/slots?date=2026-06-22 (Bearer: Patient Token)

---

## 📋 APPOINTMENT APIs

### 29. Book Appointment
POST /appointment (Bearer: Patient Token)
Body:
{
  "doctorId": "doctor-uuid",
  "date": "2026-06-22",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "10:30:00"
}

### 30. Patient Views Appointments
GET /appointment/my (Bearer: Patient Token)

### 31. Patient Cancels Appointment
PATCH /appointment/:id/cancel (Bearer: Patient Token)

### 32. Patient Reschedules Appointment
PATCH /appointment/:id/reschedule (Bearer: Patient Token)
Body:
{
  "date": "2026-06-25",
  "startTime": "11:00:00",
  "endTime": "11:30:00"
}

---

## 👨‍⚕️ DOCTOR APPOINTMENT MANAGEMENT APIs

### 33. Doctor Views All Appointments
GET /doctor/appointments (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 34. Doctor Filters Appointments by Date
GET /doctor/appointments?date=2026-06-25 (Bearer: Doctor Token)

### 35. Doctor Cancels Appointment
PATCH /doctor/appointments/:id/cancel (Bearer: Doctor Token)

---

## 🔍 NEXT AVAILABLE APPOINTMENT APIs

### 36. Check Today's Availability
GET /doctor/:doctorId/today-availability (Bearer: Patient Token)

### 37. Find Next Available Appointment
GET /doctor/:doctorId/next-available (Bearer: Patient Token)